{
  "texts": [
    "To attain such a significant vision, significant technological advancements must be made in areas such as all-optical signal processing, system optimization, and uncertainty control.",
    "These technical challenges can benefit from new theories, algorithms, and system architectures of RC.",
    "For instance, a silicon photonics integrated RC system, functioning as a photonic neural network, can achieve end-to-end optical domain signal processing with negligible power consumption and time delay in principle, without relying on electro-optical/ optical conversion.",
    "As a result, it has the potential to become a key technology in future all-optical networks.",
    "Additionally, adjusting the internal structure of the optical fiber can enable the enhancement of capacity by searching complex and diverse structures, which can benefit from the effective and automated modeling of the channel with RC."
  ]
}